<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="possible-adj">possible <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'pɒsəbl/    美 /'pɑːsəbl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>可能的</strong></h4>
<p>反 impossible: </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Anything is possible.
一切皆有可能。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>it is possible (for sb) to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It is possible for him to accomplish the task. 
他有可能完成这项任务。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>it is possible + (that) 从句：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It is possible that we have met before. 
我们可能以前见过。</p><footer>外研④ – 7</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>合理的；可接受的</strong></h4>
<p>reasonable or acceptable in a particular situation：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There are several possible explanations. 
有几种合理的解释。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>[用于形容词后表示强调] 最...的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It was the <strong>best possible</strong> surprise anyone could have given me. 
那是我曾感受过的最大的惊喜。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Don’t leave your packing until the <strong>last possible</strong> moment. 
别把打点行李拖到最后一刻。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="as-as-possible">as ... as possible</h3>
<p>1.<strong>尽可能...地：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Try to make your poster as attractive as possible.
使你的海报尽可能地吸引人。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We must take action as quickly as possible now.
我们现在必须尽快采取行动。</p><footer>2015 湖北改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You have to search for as many opportunities as possible to practice listening. 
你要寻找尽可能多的机会练习听力。</p><footer>人教⑦ – 5</footer></div>

<h3 id="if-possible">if possible</h3>
<p>1.<strong>如果可能的话：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I want to avoid the rush hour traffic if possible.
如有可能，我想避开交通高峰期。</p></div>

<h3 id="whenever-wherever-possible">whenever / wherever possible</h3>
<p>1.<strong>只要有可能；一有机会：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Use public transport whenever possible (= when you can).
只要有可能，就用公共交通工具。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Get an early start and try to be as productive <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ possible before lunch.  （2016 全国）  </li>
<li>Raymond’s parents wanted him to have the <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (good) possible education.  （2014 全国改）  </li>
<li>— Have you got any particular plans for the coming holiday?
— Yes. <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (如果可能的话), I’m going to visit some homes for the old in the city.  （2008 安徽改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. as  2. best  3. If possible  </p></div>